{{zh-forms|[[人不知，鬼不觉]]|[[人]][[不]][[知]]，[[鬼]][[不]][[覺]]}}
==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: people don't know, and ghosts don't feel

===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' rén bù zhī, guǐ bù jué)

# something that is so mysterious, that it cannot be known by humans or felt by ghosts

